@74D30  I have a couple of points i use when looking at crypto projects for longterm. Its short but has been my basic rule for a while. 
1. Is it new Algo , How long has it been out / mined if pow. What new problem is it solving , has it been done before. 
2. Supply. Some will disagree but i like a low to medium supply. Bitcoin being low supply ripple being high supply. 
3. General gut feeling of scam or not üòÇ
